00:16:50,386 --> 00:16:52,148
just sounds like noise.

330
00:16:52,148 --> 00:16:54,690
It just sounds like a fuzzy noise.

331
00:16:54,690 --> 00:16:56,591
But it's a better fuzzy noise than white noise.

332
00:16:56,591 --> 00:16:56,651
So.

