00:19:58,316 --> 00:20:03,658
With the first system in Krugman-McMulty, you knew ultimately what most likely economy

387
00:20:03,658 --> 00:20:05,859
was, but you couldn't see it coming.

388
00:20:05,859 --> 00:20:06,759
Here you can.

389
00:20:06,759 --> 00:20:10,361
You can say, okay, it's at six, it's at seven, it's getting close to that eight point.

